===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} ''[[securite]]'', from {{etyl|fro|en}} (French: {{m|fr|sécurité}}), from {{etyl|la|en}} ''[[securitas]]'', from {{etyl|la|en}} ''[[securus]]'' "[[safe]], [[secure]]", from {{affix|la|se-|gloss1=without|cura|gloss2=care|nocat=1}}; see [[cure]]. Similar to Latin {{m|la|sine cura||without care, carefree}}, which led to English {{m|en|sinecure}}.

